data.description:
Welcome to Southlake! This home is located on Brooks Base, walking distance to The Greenline Park and with views of the water. The 2 Bedroom 2 Bath end unit home has everything you're looking for. The modern design invites you in and displays luxurious finishes with a 2 car attached garage in the rear of the home. You'll walk into stained concrete floors on your first level with the utility room, second bedroom and bathroom. Head upstairs and be welcomed in by the open floor plan of the kitchen, living, dining rooms. All appliances are included in the lease, all you'll need to bring is your own furniture. The Master bedroom is on this floor as well and features a large onsuite with walk in closet, double vanity, and walk in shower.

High speed internet is included in the rent
 Walk on the gorgeous trail or to the many restaurants and shops!
